{"id":150,"parent_id":141,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":150,"title":"1 Corinthians 9","subtitle":"","short_title":"1 Cor.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 9"],[".studySummary",["i","Paul rejoices in his Christian liberty—He preaches the gospel to all without charge—He is all things to all men to gain converts."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.1","order":"03.09.009.17456"},["b","1"],"Am I not an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"apostle"],"? am I not free? have I not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"seen"],"Jesus Christ our Lord? are not ye my",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"work"],"in the Lord?"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.2","order":"03.09.009.17457"},["b","2"],"If I be not an apostle unto others, yet doubtless I am to you: for the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"seal"],"of mine apostleship are ye in the Lord."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.3","order":"03.09.009.17458"},["b","3"],"Mine",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"answer"],"to them that do",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"examine"],"me is this,"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.4","order":"03.09.009.17459"},["b","4"],"Have we not power to eat and to drink?"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.5","order":"03.09.009.17460"},["b","5"],"Have we not power to lead about a sister, a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"wife"],", as well as other apostles, and",["i","as"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"brethren"],"of the Lord, and Cephas?"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.6","order":"03.09.009.17461"},["b","6"],"Or I only and Barnabas, have not we power to forbear working?"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.7","order":"03.09.009.17462"},["b","7"],"Who goeth a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"warfare"],"any time at his own charges? who planteth a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"vineyard"],", and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"eateth"],"not of the fruit thereof? or who feedeth a flock, and eateth not of the milk of the flock?"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.8","order":"03.09.009.17463"},["b","8"],"Say I these things as a man? or saith not the law the same also?"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.9","order":"03.09.009.17464"},["b","9"],"For it is written in the law of Moses, Thou shalt not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"muzzle"],"the mouth of the ox that treadeth out the corn. Doth God take care for oxen?"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.10","order":"03.09.009.17465"},["b","10"],"Or saith he",["i","it"],"altogether for our sakes? For our sakes, no doubt,",["i","this"],"is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"written"],": that he that ploweth should plow in hope; and that he that thresheth in hope should be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"partaker"],"of his hope."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.11","order":"03.09.009.17466"},["b","11"],"If we have sown unto you",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"spiritual"],"things,",["i","is it"],"a great thing if we shall reap your carnal things?"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.12","order":"03.09.009.17467"},["b","12"],"If others be partakers of",["i","this"],"power over you,",["i","are"],"not we rather? Nevertheless we have not used this",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"power"],"; but suffer all things, lest we should hinder the gospel of Christ."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.13","order":"03.09.009.17468"},["b","13"],"Do ye not know that they which",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"minister"],"about holy things",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"live"],["i","of the things"],"of the temple? and they which wait at the altar are partakers with the altar?"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.14","order":"03.09.009.17469"},["b","14"],"Even so hath the Lord ordained that they which",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"preach"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"gospel"],"should",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"live"],"of the gospel."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.15","order":"03.09.009.17470"},["b","15"],"But I have used none of these things: neither have I written these things, that it should be so done unto me: for",["i","it were"],"better for me to die, than that any man should make my glorying void."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.16","order":"03.09.009.17471"},["b","16"],"For though I preach the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"gospel"],", I have nothing to glory of: for",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"necessity"],"is laid upon me; yea, woe is unto me, if I",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_16c"},"preach"],"not the gospel!"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.17","order":"03.09.009.17472"},["b","17"],"For if I do this thing",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"willingly"],", I have a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"reward"],": but if against my will, a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"dispensation"],["i","of the gospel"],"is committed unto me."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.18","order":"03.09.009.17473"},["b","18"],"What is my reward then?",["i","Verily"],"that, when I preach the gospel, I may make the gospel of Christ without",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"charge"],", that I abuse not my power in the gospel."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.19","order":"03.09.009.17474"},["b","19"],"For though I be free from all",["i","men,"],"yet have I made myself",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"servant"],"unto all, that I might gain the more."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.20","order":"03.09.009.17475"},["b","20"],"And unto the Jews I became as a Jew, that I might gain the Jews; to them that are under the law, as under the law, that I might gain them that are under the law;"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.21","order":"03.09.009.17476"},["b","21"],"To them that are without law, as without law, (being not without law to God, but under the law to Christ,) that I might gain them that are without law."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.22","order":"03.09.009.17477"},["b","22"],"To the weak became I as",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"weak"],", that I might gain the weak: I am made",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"all"],"things to all",["i","men,"],"that I might by all means save some."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.23","order":"03.09.009.17478"},["b","23"],"And this I do for the gospel’s sake, that I might be partaker thereof with",["i","you."]],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.24","order":"03.09.009.17479"},["b","24"],"Know ye not that they which run in a race run all, but one receiveth the prize? So run, that ye may obtain."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.25","order":"03.09.009.17480"},["b","25"],"And every man that striveth for the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"mastery"],"is",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"temperate"],"in all things. Now they",["i","do it"],"to obtain a corruptible",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_25c"},"crown"],"; but we an",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_25d"},"incorruptible"],"."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.26","order":"03.09.009.17481"},["b","26"],"I therefore so run, not as uncertainly; so fight I, not as one that beateth the air:"],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.27","order":"03.09.009.17482"},["b","27"],"But I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"keep under"],"my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_27b"},"body"],", and bring",["i","it"],"into subjection: lest that by any means, when I have preached to others, I myself should be a castaway."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.1a","order":"03.09.009.17483"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.11.11-12"},"2 Cor. 12:11 (11–12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/2.7.7-8"},"Gal. 2:7 (7–8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-tim/2.7"},"1 Tim. 2:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.1b","order":"03.09.009.17485"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/9.17.3,17"},"Acts 9:17 (3, 17)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.1.1,7"},"2 Cor. 12:1 (1, 7)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/1.12"},"Gal. 1:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.1c","order":"03.09.009.17487"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.6"},"1 Cor. 3:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.2a","order":"03.09.009.17489"},["b","2a"],["span.small","GR"],"certification, proof, token.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.2"},"2 Cor. 3:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.3a","order":"03.09.009.17491"},["b","3a"],["span.small","GR"],"defense."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.3b","order":"03.09.009.17493"},["b","3b"],["span.small","GR"],"question, call into account, judge."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.5a","order":"03.09.009.17495"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.14"},"Matt. 8:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.5b","order":"03.09.009.17497"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/12.46"},"Matt. 12:46"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.3.3,5,10"},"John 7:3 (3, 5, 10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.7a","order":"03.09.009.17499"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.4"},"2 Cor. 10:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.7b","order":"03.09.009.17501"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/20.6"},"Deut. 20:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.7c","order":"03.09.009.17503"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/27.18"},"Prov. 27:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.9a","order":"03.09.009.17505"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/25.4"},"Deut. 25:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.10a","order":"03.09.009.17507"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.4"},"Rom. 15:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.10b","order":"03.09.009.17509"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-tim/2.6.5-6"},"2 Tim. 2:6 (5–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.11a","order":"03.09.009.17511"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.27"},"Rom. 15:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.12a","order":"03.09.009.17513"},["b","12a"],["span.small","GR"],"authority."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.13a","order":"03.09.009.17515"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/18.1.1-2"},"Deut. 18:1 (1–2)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.13b","order":"03.09.009.17517"},["b","13b"],["span.small","GR"],"eat."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.14a","order":"03.09.009.17519"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/2.21.21-23"},"Rom. 2:21 (21–23)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.11.11-12"},"Alma 39:11 (11–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.14b","order":"03.09.009.17521"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/gospel"},"TG Gospel"],"."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.14c","order":"03.09.009.17523"},["b","14c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.10"},"Matt. 10:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.16a","order":"03.09.009.17525"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/gospel"},"TG Gospel"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.16b","order":"03.09.009.17527"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/duty"},"TG Duty"],"."],["div",{"id":"16c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.16c","order":"03.09.009.17529"},["b","16c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/missionary-work"},"TG Missionary Work"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/preaching"},"Preaching"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.17a","order":"03.09.009.17531"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/initiative"},"TG Initiative"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.17b","order":"03.09.009.17533"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reward"},"TG Reward"],"."],["div",{"id":"17c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.17c","order":"03.09.009.17535"},["b","17c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/2.7"},"Gal. 2:7"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/dispensations"},"TG Dispensations"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.18a","order":"03.09.009.17537"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/20.34.33-34"},"Acts 20:34 (33–34)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/11.7"},"2 Cor. 11:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.9"},"1 Thes. 2:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/2.14.12,14-18"},"Mosiah 2:14 (12, 14–18)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.19a","order":"03.09.009.17539"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.5"},"2 Cor. 4:5"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/servant"},"TG Servant"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.22a","order":"03.09.009.17541"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/11.29"},"2 Cor. 11:29"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.22b","order":"03.09.009.17543"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/10.33.32-33"},"1 Cor. 10:33 (32–33)"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.25a","order":"03.09.009.17545"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-tim/2.5"},"2 Tim. 2:5"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/self-mastery"},"TG Self-Mastery"],"."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.25b","order":"03.09.009.17547"},["b","25b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/temperance"},"TG Temperance"],"."],["div",{"id":"25c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.25c","order":"03.09.009.17549"},["b","25c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reward"},"TG Reward"],"."],["div",{"id":"25d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.25d","order":"03.09.009.17551"},["b","25d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/1.4.1-16"},"1 Pet. 1:4 (1–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.27a","order":"03.09.009.17553"},["b","27a"],["span.small","GR"],"rigorously discipline."],["div",{"id":"27b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.27b","order":"03.09.009.17555"},["b","27b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/chastity"},"TG Chastity"],"."]]}
